title: Numismata Summorum Pontificum Templi Vaticani Fabricam Indicantia, Chronologica ejusden Fabricae narratione, ac multiplici eruditione explicata, Atque uberiori Numismatum omnium Pontificiorum Lucubrationi veluti Prodromus praemissa A Patre Philippo
medium: 1 vol: ill: 88 etching and engravings (12 folding, rest full-page, versos blank), artists include Giovanni Battista Lenardi, Giovanni Girolamo Frezza, Carlo Patacchia, Alessandro Specchi, Arnold van Westerhout, Pietro Santo Bartoli, Jean Charles Allet
dimensions: page size: 36 x 24.5 cm (14 3/16 x 9 5/8 in.)
